my retirement account.

10:12.833 --> 10:14.267
Did you bring
the cashier's check?

10:14.367 --> 10:16.367
- Right here.
- Cool.

10:16.467 --> 10:18.700
Beautiful, beautiful home.
Wow.

10:18.800 --> 10:21.533
Hello, I'm Forrest.
This is my producer, Grant.

10:21.633 --> 10:23.133
Hey, Joe,
if that's your wife,

10:23.233 --> 10:24.333
we should just
make sure she's not--

10:24.433 --> 10:25.867
- That's not my wife.
- Oh, okay.

10:25.967 --> 10:26.833
Oh, you know what?
I didn't even ask you.

10:26.933 --> 10:32.033
do you get Skype here?

10:32.133 --> 10:33.333
