getting into her backstory.

11:43.833 --> 11:45.600
Not to get too much
into my backstory,

11:45.700 --> 11:46.867
but I spent a lot of years

11:46.967 --> 11:49.333
with the guy who I thought
I was meant to be with,

11:49.433 --> 11:51.300
and so much of that just

11:51.400 --> 11:53.600
