than Joe Dale Jr. could handle.

12:04.333 --> 12:06.833
Hey, Suzanne,
my name's not Ace.

12:06.933 --> 12:08.167
- What?
- It's Joe Dale Jr.

12:08.267 --> 12:09.233
[whispers]
No! Hey!

12:09.333 --> 12:10.333
