but I can't.

12:19.067 --> 12:21.933
Whatever begins with dishonesty
always ends in a bad spot.

12:22.067 --> 12:23.200
Trust me, I know.

12:23.300 --> 12:24.767
I'm a baseball player.

12:24.867 --> 12:25.967
(Forrest)
And then Joe, for some reason,

12:26.067 --> 12:28.700
